nodes.text: House Indupar was an Ancient House that headed the Induparan Monarchy and ruled over the Induparan Crown Worlds. The House was led by King Dahon Indupar during the Galactic Civil War. In the Ec Pand system (counted among the Crown Worlds) a noble of House Indupar, Lady Kalena, was captured by the Rebel privateer Urias Xhaxin and held to ransom.
